com.couchbase.client.java.query

Class AsyncQueryResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.couchbase.client.java.query.AsyncQueryResult

  • @Stability.Volatile
public class AsyncQueryResult
extends Object
    Query Result that fetches the parts of the Query response asynchronously
    Since:
    3.0.0

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      AsyncQueryResult(QueryResponse response) 

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Concrete Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Optional<String> clientContextId()
      Returns the client context identifier string set on the query request, if it's available
      CompletableFuture<QueryMetrics> metrics()
      A CompletableFuture which completes with the the QueryMetrics as returned by the query engine The future can complete successfully or throw an ExecutionException wrapping - DecodingFailedException when the decoding of the part of the response failed
      CompletableFuture<JsonObject> profileInfo()
      A CompletableFuture which completes with profiling information as returned by the query engine which are then decoded to JsonObject The future can complete successfully or throw an ExecutionException wrapping - DecodingFailedException when the request cannot be completed successfully
      CompletableFuture<String> queryStatus()
      A CompletableFuture which completes with the query execution status as returned by the query engine
      String requestId()
      Returns the request identifier string of the query request
      CompletableFuture<List<JsonObject>> rows()
      A CompletableFuture which completes with the query execution status as returned by the query engine The future can complete successfully or throw an ExecutionException wrapping - DecodingFailedException when the decoding cannot be completed successfully
      <T> CompletableFuture<List<T>> rows(Class<T> target)
      A CompletableFuture which completes with the query execution status as returned by the query engine The future can complete successfully or throw an ExecutionException wrapping - DecodingFailedException when the decoding cannot be completed successfully
      JsonObject signature()
      A CompletableFuture which completes with the signature as returned by the query engine which are then decoded to JsonObject The future can complete successfully or throw an ExecutionException wrapping - DecodingFailedException when the request cannot be completed successfully
      CompletableFuture<List<JsonObject>> warnings()
      A CompletableFuture which completes with the list of query execution warnings as returned by the query engine which are then decoded to JsonObject The future can complete successfully or throw an ExecutionException wrapping - DecodingFailedException when the decoding cannot be completed successfully
